quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,"Boola mbu; “enywe Abandu! Ni muli nende obukanakani khudini yanje, esie shelamanga ebiamulaamanga habundu wa Nyasaye tawe, halali elaamanga Nyasaye ulia ulibafwisia ne yanomesiyie mbu embe mubasuubili.”"
  10,105,"Ne ohenjie obweni bubwo khu idini yokhutswenulila emilukha chichio khu Nyasaye, ne olaba mubatsokaasinjia Nyasaye tawe"
  10,106,"Ne olalaama ebilali Nyasaye, bilakhakhukhoonya nohomba okhumisia tawe, ne nokhola orio olaba mubandu ababii"
  10,107,"Ne Nyasaye nakhutilakhwo khububii, abulaho yesiyesi unyala okhurusiliaho libii elo owulali ye tawe, ne nakhwenyela amalayi abulaho unyala okhukalusia obulayi bwaye, ahelesinjia owayenya mubandu bebe, naye ni Omunji wobulesheli Omunji wetsimbabaasi"
  10,108,"Boola mbu; “Enywe Abandu toto obwatoto bumalile okhuboolela okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu. Kho ulia ulunjikha alunjikhanga khululwe omwene, naye ulia ukora akoranga khululwe omwene. Nasi shendi omulindi khwinywe tawe"
  10,109,"Ne loonda akofimbulilungwa, ne wisumulisie okhula shingala Nyasaye alabusia, Naye niye Omubusia Omulayi muno umalayo"